_root.charBiography = new Object();
_root.charBiography.Captain = "Captain Gundam is the secret defender of Neotopia. His identity is a secret, and the citizens aren\'t aware of his existence. He has been given special clearance to use a wide variety of weapons to defend his homeland. However, his most powerful asset proves to be the Soul Drive, which is activated when he first meets Shute. Heroic and brave, Captain is also a little stiff and doesn\'t always understand emotions. He is a perfect fighting machine.";
_root.charBiography.Zero = "Zero is a Knight Gundam from the world of Lacroa. His homeland was invaded by the Dark Axis, and although he and his comrades fought bravely, they ultimately were defeated. At his princess\'s command, he left to find a way to defeat the Dark Axis. Zero is a powerful sorcerer, and often uses magic to devastate the enemy forces. A gallant hero, he has a weakness for protecting damsels in distress, and hates to be made fun of.";
_root.charBiography.Bakunetsumaru = "Bakunetsumaru is a Musha Gundam from the land of Ark. His homeworld is in the midst of a civil war. The Dark Axis has taken advantage of this and is supporting the evil warlord Kibaomaru. Bakunetsumaru only wants to return home and defend his world. Although he is an excellent swordsman, he is very hot-headed and quick to anger. He and Zero spend a lot of time arguing.";
